# Writing Professional Emails Template  
## Instructions for Use -- DELETE WHEN USING FOR ACTUAL PROMPT  
This is only an example prompt template, so you may customize it to fit your  
prompt.  
However, your prompt here must at the very least include:  
- Description of the prompt's purpose and usage  
- A TASK statement of what the AI to do  
- Your actual prompt, organized in meaningful categories, such as Context, Output,  
Format, Constraints, etc.  
- You must include [PLACEHOLDER] in square brackets and in caps.  
---  
## The Prompt  
I work at [ Where you work ] and am writing an email to [person you're emailing] regarding [ what the email is about ] I would like it to be [ how many words in the email ]. Make the email [ friendly, professional, etc]. 
**Placeholders**    
- **Where you work:** write the job you are writing the email for.
- **Person you're emailing:** The persons occupation as related to the email.
- **What the email is about:** Write why you are writing the email and what you need in the email. 
- **How many words in the email:** Put the number of words you want for the email, it will probably not be exact so give a rough estimate of the words you want, like less than 60.
- **Friendly, professional, etc:** Write what you want the email to reflect.
